ZH: 人山人海，到处都是人。
EN: The place is crowded with people everywhere.

ZH: 人生苦短，珍惜每一天。
EN: Life is short, cherish every day.

ZH: 这个世界上的人群是如此多样化。
EN: The people in this world are so diverse.

ZH: 去公园散步能看到很多人。
EN: You can see a lot of people walking in the park.

ZH: 人类对自然环境造成了很大的破坏。
EN: Humans have caused great damage to the natural environment.

ZH: 我一直认为恶人会受到报应。
EN: I have always believed that evil people will be punished.

ZH: 这个村庄里的人口正在快速增长。
EN: The population in this village is growing rapidly.

ZH: 人不可貌相，表面有时会欺骗人。
EN: Don't judge a book by its cover, appearances can sometimes deceive.

ZH: 我认为人类是地球上最聪明的生物。
EN: I believe that humans are the most intelligent beings on Earth.

ZH: 请记得关心弱势群体中的人。
EN: Please remember to care for the marginalized people.

ZH: 出门在外一个人也不容易。
EN: It's not easy to be alone away from home.

ZH: 人们需要娱乐来放松自己。
EN: People need entertainment to relax.

ZH: 这个城市的人口密度很高。
EN: The population density of this city is very high.

ZH: 人的思维方式有时会受到环境的影响。
EN: Human thinking can sometimes be influenced by the environment.

ZH: 这个国家的土地适合人类居住。
EN: The land of this country is suitable for human habitation.

ZH: 人们需要相互尊重来维持和谐社会。
EN: People need to respect each other to maintain a harmonious society.

ZH: 一群人聚在一起讨论未来的计划。
EN: A group of people gathered together to discuss future plans.

ZH: 过多地服用药物对人体健康有害。
EN: Overuse of medication can be harmful to human health.

ZH: 无论发生什么事，人们都会互相支持。
EN: No matter what happens, people will support each other.

ZH: 我们应该为人类的未来负责。
EN: We should take responsibility for the future of humanity.
